## 4. Protection of the brainTerms.ai Platform

The brainTerms.ai platform, including:
- agent architectures  
- digital‑twin simulation engines  
- proprietary orchestration systems  
- UI/UX workflows  
- system logic or backend implementations  

is **not** open‑sourced and remains  
**© brainTerms.ai — All Rights Reserved**.

Nothing in this repository grants rights to:
- reverse engineer  
- replicate  
- emulate  
- or commercially compete with  

the proprietary operational platform of brainTerms.ai.

---

## 5. Intent of This Licensing Model

This licensing structure is designed to:

✅ Promote global adoption of the SAFIR 5C™ methodology  
✅ Encourage academic and professional use  
✅ Ensure derivative research remains open  
✅ Protect the SAFIR 5C™ brand from dilution  
✅ Preserve the integrity and authority of brainTerms.ai as the official implementation  
✅ Prevent misuse, confusion, or misattribution in commercial contexts  

By contributing to or using this repository, you agree to respect these terms.

